<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 09:12:42 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>瑞信中国证券合资公司称2023年员工人数将减少46%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-china-securities-jv-says-staff-down-46-2023-2024-05-04/</link><description>瑞士信贷在中国的证券经纪合资企业表示，2023 年其员工人数将减少 46%，这一年瑞士当局安排了一次收购，以防止该公司倒闭。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 08:05:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/credit-suisse-china-securities-jv-says-staff-down-46-2023-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>印度外交部长拒绝拜登的“仇外”言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-foreign-minister-rejects-bidens-xenophobia-comment-2024-05-04/</link><description>据《经济时报》周六报道，印度外交部长苏杰生驳斥了美国总统乔·拜登有关“仇外心理”阻碍印度经济增长的言论。</description><pubDate>Sat, 04 May 2024 05:34:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/indias-foreign-minister-rejects-bidens-xenophobia-comment-2024-05-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国 Zeekr 在美国 IPO 寻求高达 51.3 亿美元的估值</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zeekr-plans-raise-up-368-mln-us-ipo-2024-05-03/</link><description>电动汽车制造商Zeekr智能科技控股公司周五表示，其在美国首次公开募股(IPO)的目标估值高达51.3亿美元，这是两年多来中国公司首次大规模上市。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 21:21:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-zeekr-plans-raise-up-368-mln-us-ipo-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>小久保在伤停补时扑出点球，为日本队锁定冠军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kokubos-injury-time-penalty-save-secures-title-japan-2024-05-03/</link><description>日本队在周五以 1-0 击败乌兹别克斯坦队后，在伤停补时阶段由小久保扑出点球，为大岩刚的球队夺得了 23 岁以下亚洲杯冠军。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 20:56:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/kokubos-injury-time-penalty-save-secures-title-japan-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>流亡中国商人的幕僚长在美国承认欺诈罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/exiled-chinese-businessmans-chief-of-staff-pleads-guilty-us-fraud-2024-05-03/</link><description>流亡中国商人郭文贵的幕僚长周五承认与郭文贵合谋实施一项大规模计划，诈骗数千名投资者超过 10 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 17:57:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/exiled-chinese-businessmans-chief-of-staff-pleads-guilty-us-fraud-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大调查发现外国干预选举的证据，但结果不受影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-probe-finds-evidence-foreign-meddling-elections-results-not-affected-2024-05-03/</link><description>根据周五公布的初步调查结果，官方调查发现加拿大最近两次联邦选举有外国干预的证据，但投票结果没有受到影响，选举制度也很健全。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 16:58:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/canada-probe-finds-evidence-foreign-meddling-elections-results-not-affected-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯称美国二次制裁旨在“遏制”中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-us-secondary-sanctions-aim-contain-china-2024-05-03/</link><description>俄罗斯外交部发言人玛丽亚·扎哈罗娃(Maria Zakharova)周五表示，美国正在利用对被视为与俄罗斯接触的中国企业实施二次制裁的威胁作为试图遏制北京的“借口”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 15:32:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/russia-says-us-secondary-sanctions-aim-contain-china-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>汽车制造商赢得了在电动汽车税收抵免中使用中国石墨的延期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</link><description>美国财政部周五为汽车制造商提供了对来自中国的一些重要微量矿物（例如石墨）的电动汽车税收抵免的电池矿物要求的额外灵活性。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 14:12:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/automakers-win-extension-use-chinese-graphite-ev-tax-credits-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>习近平访问之前，中国在法国电动汽车市场的份额下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</link><description>行业数据显示，法国政府减缓中国制造电动汽车涌入的努力正在取得成果，这突显了中国国家主席下周访问时最敏感的贸易问题之一。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 12:24:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-share-french-ev-market-slumps-after-incentives-curbed-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟称三家中国电动汽车制造商提供的信息不足</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-information-three-chinese-ev-makers-insufficient-2024-05-03/</link><description>据两位知情人士透露，欧盟委员会已警告三家中国电动汽车制造商，称他们没有为其反补贴调查提供足够的信息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:04:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-says-information-three-chinese-ev-makers-insufficient-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>苹果股价上涨，创纪录的回购和乐观的预测吸引了投资者</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-shares-jump-record-buyback-sales-growth-forecast-lure-investors-2024-05-03/</link><description>苹果股价周五上涨 7%，这家 iPhone 制造商创纪录的股票回购计划和销售增长的承诺吸引了因担心中国需求疲软和竞争加剧而回避该股的投资者。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 11:00:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-shares-jump-record-buyback-sales-growth-forecast-lure-investors-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>尽管价格下跌，但亚洲黄金消费大国印度和中国的黄金需求仍低迷</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-demand-subdued-top-consumers-india-china-despite-price-drop-2024-05-03/</link><description>印度的实物黄金需求本周仍然低迷，尽管价格略有调整，因为买家等待更大的跌幅，而中国的溢价由于假期需求低迷而连续第二周下滑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:23:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asia-gold-demand-subdued-top-consumers-india-china-despite-price-drop-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：乔布斯测试美联储的救济措施、苹果回购的冲击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-03/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 10:02:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>中国启动历史性月球背面采样任务</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/china-launches-historic-mission-retrieve-samples-far-side-moon-2024-05-03/</link><description>中国周五发射了一艘无人驾驶飞船，执行了近两个月的任务，从月球背面取回岩石和土壤，这是第一个进行如此雄心勃勃的尝试的国家。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 09:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/china-launches-historic-mission-retrieve-samples-far-side-moon-2024-05-03/</guid></item><item><title>美国国防部长称，菲律宾在南海造成的损害是“不负责任的行为”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/damage-injury-philippines-south-china-sea-is-irresponsible-behaviour-says-us-2024-05-03/</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀周四在谈到涉及中国的最新冲突时表示，在南中国海对菲律宾船只造成损害并造成船员受伤是无视国际法的“不负责任的行为”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 03 May 2024 03:08:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/damage-injury-philippines-south-china-sea-is-irresponsible-behaviour-says-us-2024-05-03/</guid></item></channel></rss>